Definitions

1. A "Creator Instance" is a Reddit user account which is operated and
maintained by original author of this source code and is used by the
Program for processing and replying to comments.
2. A subreddit where a Creator Instance has ability to submit comments
to is referred to as "Covered Subreddit".

